      "commonsTitle": "File:Crowded Train Platform During 9-Euro Ticket Period in Germany.jpg",
      "commonsPage": "https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File%3ACrowded_Train_Platform_During_9-Euro_Ticket_Period_in_Germany.jpg",
      "downloadedFrom": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/aa/Crowded_Train_Platform_During_9-Euro_Ticket_Period_in_Germany.jpg/1280px-Crowded_Train_Platform_During_9-Euro_Ticket_Period_in_Germany.jpg",
      "sourceOriginal": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/aa/Crowded_Train_Platform_During_9-Euro_Ticket_Period_in_Germany.jpg",
      "width": 1280,
      "height": 960,
      "bytes": 463628,
      "mime": "image/jpeg",
      "author": "Spinarak",
      "license": "CC0",
      "licenseUrl": "http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/deed.en",
      "credit": "Own work",
      "description": "This image captures a crowded scene at a train platform in Germany during the 9-euro ticket period, an initiative by the German government in the summer of 2022 to encourage public transportation use by offering unlimited monthly travel for only 9 euros. The platform is filled with passengers, and many are seen boarding or disembarking from the regional train. The photo highlights the popularity of the 9-euro ticket, which led to significantly increased use of public transport. The architecture of the station roof is also visible, framing the busy crowd."
